        <div class="w3-third">
          <!-- Right Third -->
          <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity" style="height:35%; width:100%;" onclick="location.href='/t?src=home&dst=rightposter';"></button>
          <div class="w3-row">
            <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity w3-half" style="height:65%;" onclick="location.href='/t?src=home&dst=recreational';"></button>
            <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity w3-half" style="height:65%;" onclick="location.href='/t?src=home&dst=artistic';"></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>



      <!-- LAST -->
      <div class="w3-display-bottommiddle w3-center cm-scroll-indicator w3-large w3-hide-small" style="transform: translate(-50%, -350%)">
        Read more <br>
        <img src="/static/triangle.png" alt="" style="width:4%;">
      </div>
      <div class="w3-display-topleft w3-container cm-button w3-round" onclick="location.href='/help'" style="width:50px; height:50px;">
        <div class="w3-display-container" style="width:100%; height:100%;">
          <div class="w3-display-middle">
            ?
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- infopane -->
    <div class="w3-container cm-infopane">
      <div class="cm-h1 w3-center">
        Quick links
      </div>
      <div class="w3-container">
        <% [{"title":"Static Display Items", "dest":"static"},
            {"title":"Dynamic Display Items", "dest":"dynamic"},
            {"title":"Left Poster", "dest":"leftposter"},
            {"title":"Left Legs and Screen", "dest":"leftlegs"},
            {"title":"Printer", "dest":"printer"},
            {"title":"Right Legs and Screen", "dest":"rightlegs"},
            {"title":"Right Poster", "dest":"rightposter"},
            {"title":"Recreational Display Items", "dest":"recreational"},
            {"title":"Artistic Display Items", "dest":"artistic"}].forEach(function(link){ %>
              <div class="w3-container w3-center w3-cell w3-mobile">
                <a href="/t?src=home&dst=<%=link.dest;%>"> <%=link.title%> </a>
              </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>

      <!-- HEADER SECTION -->
      <div class="cm-h1 w3-center">
        Additive Manufacturing Kiosk
      </div>
      This kiosk is designed to create an experience where you can learn about the everyday benefits of additive manufacturing and how this futuristic technology is something that everyone can utilize. Each element of the kiosk has been thoughtfully designed to engage multiple senses to explore additive manufacturing.
      <hr>

      <!-- CONTENT -->
      <div class="w3-container w3-center cm-textbox">
        <div class="cm-h1 w3-center">
          Documentary
        </div>
        This short documentary shows the CMTC team's process in creating this experience both in the physical and the virtual spaces.
        <br>
        <iframe width="100%" height="100%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fKZb4pSLoOM" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>

