        <button class="w3-button cm-button" onclick="expand('ar')" style="width:50%;">// App / AR Integration //</button>
        <div id="ar" class="w3-container w3-round-large cm-acordian w3-hide">
          Augmented Reality (AR) is an interactive experience where computer generated graphics can be manifested within live camera feeds such as on a phone. In practice, this can be seen in examples such as the popular mobile game Pokémon Go which uses AR to show the users the real world with videogame characters added in. Other examples include auto manufacturers allowing customers to see what's under the hood without actually having to open it.
          <br>
          AR is a fun component of the AM Kiosk! Download the app below to access the full potential of this Kiosk as well as the AR capabilities.
          <br>

          <div class="w3-center">
            <a href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/iJlZcYOz">
              <img src="/static/appstore.svg" alt="" style="width:200px;" class="w3-image" onclick="location.href='https://testflight.apple.com/join/iJlZcYOz'">
            </a>
            <br> <br>
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.CMTC.WindowToMars">
              <img src="/static/playstore.png" alt="" style="width:200px;" class="w3-image">
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>

        <button class="w3-button cm-button" onclick="expand('about')" style="width:50%;">// Meet the CMTC Team //</button>
        <div id="about" class="w3-container w3-round-large cm-acordian w3-hide">
          <% members.forEach(function(member, i){ %>
            <div class="w3-row w3-center w3-container" stlye="margins: 10px; width:100%; height: 100%;">
              <% if(i % 2 == 0){ %>
                <div class="w3-third" style="height: 400px;">
                  <img src="/static/team/<%=member.image%>" class="w3-image w3-round" style="height: 400px;">
                </div>
                <div class="w3-twothird" style="height: 400px;">
                  <div class="w3-display-container" style="height: inherit;">
                    <div class="w3-display-middle">
                      <div class="cm-h1">
                        <%= member.name %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="cm-text">
                        <%= member.title %>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <% } else { %>
                <div class="w3-twothird" style="height: 400px;">
                  <div class="w3-display-container" style="height: inherit;">
                    <div class="w3-display-middle">
                      <div class="cm-h1">
                        <%= member.name %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="cm-text">
                        <%= member.title %>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w3-third" style="height: 400px;">
                  <img src="/static/team/<%=member.image%>" class="w3-image w3-round" style="height: 400px;">
                </div>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          <% }) %>
